%p Access Controls grant a set of permissions for a set of data to a set of users.  Permissions are attached to Roles, data access is granted through Collections and users are assigned via User Groups.
.row
  .col-6
    = f.input :role_id, as: :select_two, label_method: :name, collection: Role.editable
    = f.input :collection_id, as: :select_two, label_method: :name, collection: Collection.general
    = f.input :user_group_id, as: :select_two, label_method: :name, collection: UserGroup.not_system
